Construction Materials

Company Overview of Kilgore Companies, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Kilgore Companies, LLC, through its subsidiaries, engages in the production, sale, and supply of concrete, aggregate, and other building products. The company offers ready mix concrete, concrete wall blocks, concrete steps and tables, landscape and parking blocks, aggregate materials, asphalt, sand and gravel, and pre cast products. It also provides services, such as pumping, earthworks, equipment rental and service, heavy construction, paving, logistics, remediation, retail (construction/oilfield supply), road construction, site development, and septic tank and underground utility works. Kilgore Companies, LLC was formerly known as Harper-Kilgore, LLC and changed its name to Kilgore Compani...
Kilgore Companies, LLC, through its subsidiaries, engages in the production, sale, and supply of concrete, aggregate, and other building products. The company offers ready mix concrete, concrete wall blocks, concrete steps and tables, landscape and parking blocks, aggregate materials, asphalt, sand and gravel, and pre cast products. It also provides services, such as pumping, earthworks, equipment rental and service, heavy construction, paving, logistics, remediation, retail (construction/oilfield supply), road construction, site development, and septic tank and underground utility works. Kilgore Companies, LLC was formerly known as Harper-Kilgore, LLC and changed its name to Kilgore Companies, LLC in December 2010. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in West Valley City, Utah with an additional office in West Twin Falls, Idaho. It also has operations in Wyoming, Utah, and Idaho. Kilgore Companies, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Summit Materials, LLC.
