ShareOverviewSummaryKilgore Companies LLC has worked on seven contracts worth $14.7 million USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2015), the organization received a total of -$35 USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Defense, Department of the Interior, and Department of Transportation.* A negative obligation amount is a de-obligation, meaning the money was given back to the federal government.

