Overview Kilgore Companies LLC is a ready-mixed concrete company in West Valley City, Utah. The organization is located at 7057 W 2100 S. This private company was founded in 1993 (about 24 years ago).Revenue The organization generates $19.9M in estimated sales.Employees Kilgore Companies LLC employs 99 people. In West Valley City, an average company has between 2 and 29 employees, meaning that slightly more people work at Kilgore Companies LLC than at the average company.
 





