              About Kilgore Flares
            


Kilgore Flares Company is a world leader in the design, development and manufacture of advanced expendable countermeasures and countermeasure suites, and serves as the sole-source IR decoy flare supplier for some of the worlds most sophisticated and advanced airborne platforms.




