Summit Materials













 
  






Kilgore Companies












Through this company collaboration we are able to offer our customers an integrated product offering.Summit formed Kilgore Companies in 2010 which is now comprised of: Kilgore Paving, Harper Contracting, Altaview Concrete, EnerCrest, Triple C Concrete, Elam, B&B, Grand Junction Pipe, LeGrand Johnson Construction Company, Lewis & Lewis, Sandco, Sierra Ready-Mix, and Westroc. This combination of companies gives us significant presence in Utah, Colorado, Idaho, Nevada, and Wyoming expanding our western reach. Kilgore Paving has been operating in the greater Salt Lake City area for over 15 years, and the company and work is renowned for it's excellent work.
